      "text": "But the wicked shall perish, And the enemies of Jehovah shall be as the fat of lambs: They shall consume; in smoke shall they consume away.",
      "versionTitle": "American Standard Version"
    },
    {
      "language": "en",
      "ref": "Psalm 37:20",
      "source_id": "web",
